De_elysion is a port of the De_elysion map from the CSGO game.

Also, additional map optimization has been done.

De_elysion took 7th place on the 2020 wingman mapping contest.

Original map description:

Terrorists have infiltrated Elysion on the 39th floor and are ready to plant explosives in the main hall where the building is the weakest. Everybody has already evacuated the building and it is up to the security force to stop the terrorists at all cost.

D E _ E L I I T T I S A U N A

By NakkiMaisteri

OBJECTIVE

Terrorists: Plant the bomb to the sauna located in middle of the map.!
Counter terrorists: Protect the sauna from demolition by all cost!

MAP INFORMATION

Map has special "spawn area" where all players have 60 seconds to choose their "class" and buy their gear, if the time expires and the player is still at spawn area, the player will die.

Classes are: 
1. Speed: + Minor speed, - Minor damage
2. Recon: + Major Invisibility, - Major damage
3. Heavy: + Heavy machinegun, - Minor speed
If you don't wish to have a class you can just walk forward to the pit and have default stats.

Whole map is completely symmetrical.
Map doesn't have light sources, since this map's gonna be more about performance than looking good.

Map contains: "Single bomb site / "Class" system / High FPS" Recommented players/Max players: 24/34 
Spawnpoints: Both teams will spawn next to each other in a "Spawn area".
All of the map isn't in the screenshots, EXPLORE!

Download --> Test --> Comment --> Rate.

Kittehs will thank you!

De_Egyptkm - A CS:S Map by [KM] The Husband aka DeMoNeye - V1.0
-----------------------------------------------------------------

Following the greatest sandstorm in history, the undiscovered Ancient Egyptian city of Herpestes Ichneumon has risen from the dunes!

Separatist terrorists are trying to bomb the recently discovered artifacts for fear of their ancient powers!

Counter Terrorists Units have deployed and must stop the terrorists at all costs.

Special Thanks Clan[KM] (all the guys there), [KM]ShadowDog, [UF]Extreme_0ne, [UF]Gee and of course [KM] The Wife - how could I miss her off!

(Look out for the special button to let you into the "Amok Time" 1v1 area!!!)

Story:
The Counter-Terrorists have tracked down
a group of Terrorists who are raiding 
a secret area in the middle of Egypt.
The Terrorists have no choice but to
evacuate but wont leave without blowing
the base to pieces first.

Authors note:
I created the map due to a few of my favorite
servers using zm_lila_panic as a fightyard map.
I really hated the poor quality of the map so made
a version which had same gameplay but also looked
decent. I did add 1 new route but it was just to balance
the gameplay out. The new route gives the Terrorist
team a 60% better chance of survival, the other route
is from the original layout and was always the rush point
for the Counter-Terrorists team. Also i spent a long time
on optimizing the map so it will output around the same fps.

Other notes:
64 Spawn points|32 each team.
1 Main bombsite.
Nav inside the bsp.
Protected from Decompile.
